PrecisORDER OF CONSENT - THE TRAVELERS, INC. - which authorizes The Travelers, Inc., a foreign bank, to indirectly establish a new Canadian business by the indirect acquisition and holding of shares in Smith Barney Canada Inc. and to indirectly acquire and hold shares in the latter in such a number as to cause it to become a non-bank affiliate of a foreign bank.
